&lt;h2 id="experimenting-abstraction-of-an-abstract-image"&gt;Experimenting - abstraction of an abstract image&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But what happens when you look very closely at an abstract image, what hidden parts of it might reveal something entirely new ? All you have to do is to look closer, seriously the experiment below is mainly based on zooming and secondarily on applying diferent filters to emphasize the shapes comming into view.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In this case this image will tell a story but of a different type, That of how a computer creates displays an image. When you zoom in an image pixels are either enlarged (ex Photoshop) or resampled (preview in mac)&lt;/p&gt;

